OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FPolitical correspondent Elaine Wilcox
OL,8,Fhas the latest on two North West MPs
OL,9,Fwho have been suspended from the
OL,10,FLabour party.
OL,12,FAn MP suspended by her party after
OL,13,Fbacking an amendment to scrap the two-
OL,14,Fchild benefit cap says she was
OL,15,Fspeaking "for her constituents" who
OL,16,F"have no voice".
OL,18,FRebecca Long-Bailey is one of seven
OL,19,FMPs who had the whip removed by Keir
OL,20,FStarmer for voting against the
OL,21,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
