OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe Salford representative joins
OL,8,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne,
OL,9,FApsana Begum, Richard Burgon, Imran
OL,10,FHussain, John McDonnell and Zarah
OL,11,FSultana who have all also been
OL,12,Fsuspended from the party for six
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FIn a statement Ms Long-Bailey said she
OL,16,Fhad "urged" the government "to scrap
OL,17,Fthe two-child limit on Universal
OL,18,FCredit", saying it was an issue "many
OL,19,Fstruggling families" had raised with
OL,20,Fher.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
