OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"Scrapping the two-child limit would
OL,8,Flift hundreds of thousands of children
OL,9,Facross the country out of poverty.
OL,11,F"I support the King's Speech and
OL,12,Fsupport Government pledges to roll out
OL,13,Fbreakfast clubs and to instigate a
OL,14,Fchild poverty task force.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
