OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"I am gravely concerned however that
OL,8,Fthis will take considerable time to
OL,9,Fpass through the relevant stages of
OL,10,Fconsultation and indeed into final
OL,11,Flegislation. That is why I voted in
OL,12,Ffavour of scrapping the two-child
OL,13,Flimit.
OL,15,F"I am deeply saddened to have had the
OL,16,Fwhip suspended for six months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
