OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"As a strict matter of conscience, on
OL,8,Fthis occasion I felt I must speak for
OL,9,Fmy constituents who have no voice in
OL,10,Fthe hope that the Government urgently
OL,11,Fhelps them on this issue.
OL,13,F"I will continue to work with the
OL,14,FGovernment and colleagues to help the
OL,15,Fconstituents I represent."
