OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FFellow MP Ian Byrne said he too had
OL,8,Fvoted against the government after
OL,9,Fexperts told him it was the "best way
OL,10,Fto immediately impact" figures which
OL,11,Fshowed 43% of children in his
OL,12,Fconstituency live in poverty.
OL,14,FDuring Starmer's first Prime
OL,15,FMinister's Questions, he faced
OL,16,Fquestions from two SNP MPs over his
OL,17,Fdecision to suspend those who rebelled.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
