OL,3,C'I spoke for my constituents who have
OL,4,Cno voice': Party-suspended MP speaks
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe cap, introduced in 2015 by then-
OL,8,FConservative chancellor George
OL,9,FOsborne, restricts child welfare
OL,10,Fpayments to the first two children
OL,11,Fborn to most families.
OL,13,FA report from the End Child Poverty
OL,14,FCoalition in June found child poverty
OL,15,Frates are directly and strongly
OL,16,Fcorrelated with the percentage of
OL,17,Fchildren affected by the two-child
OL,18,Flimit in the local area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
